						p Queue-jump? Punting? Early bird? Our admin panel allows you to create as many ticket types as you can think of, and decide exactly who can buy them and at the times you want. [check]
					.col-md-6.whatboxsm
						.title
							span.fa.fa-mobile
							h4 #[span.h  Mobile first]
						p Mabel looks great on mobile, so students can book their tickets from the comfort of their college library.
				.row
